itemDescription: British Egyptologist, papyrologist, Anglican priest, and academic

wikipedia_page.main: John Wintour Baldwin Barns (12 May 1912 – 23 February 1974) was a British Egyptologist, papyrologist, Anglican priest, and academic. From 1965 to 1974, he was Professor of Egyptology at the University of Oxford.
